This is how to common of l1 and l2:
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this l1's length times:
    Remember that x is item i in l1
    When x is in l2, then:
      When x is not in result, then:
        Add result to x
      End when
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  Remember that sorted is []
  Do this result's length times:
    Remember that min_value is nothing
    Remember that min_index is 0
    Remember that j is 0
    Do this result's length times:
      Remember that y is item j in result
      When y is not nothing, then:
        When min_value is nothing, then:
          Remember that min_value is y
          Remember that min_index is j
        But, if not:
          When y is less than min_value, then:
            Remember that min_value is y
            Remember that min_index is j
          End when
        End when
      End when
